status.description: A resolution has been taken, and it is awaiting verification by reporter. From here issues are either reopened, or are closed.
status.name: Resolved

fields.description:
*+Objective+*
 * Room number filter to make ND unit selection more efficient
 * Room number filter default selected leverage referrer info for seamless user journey

*+Implementation+*
 * If there is referrer information, we will select the # of room accordingly.
 * If there is no referrer information, we select total and show all listing.
 * When # of unit is more than 10, we will fold it and show view more for user to unfold it.
 * When user clicks the filter, we will only show that type of unit.
 * UI update according to mock-up; when there is empty value for some attributes, we show "0".
 * We won't do reply to unit in this version.

*+Mock-up+*
 * Desktop -  zpl.io/blmye9e
 * Mobile - zpl.io/bPdMBrM
fields.summary: Add option for applications to register a custom server selector

* Room number filter to make ND unit selection more efficient
* Room number filter default selected leverage referrer info for seamless user journey

*+Implementation+*

* We won't do reply to unit in this version.
